| task_id           | int(11)    | NO   | MUL | NULL    |       |
| started/finished  | tinyint(1) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| reviewer_id       | int(11)    | YES  | MUL | NULL    |       |
| rejected/accepted | tinyint(1) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
+-------------------+------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
5 rows in set (0.00 sec)

